Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:32.67,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ff80}誰もいない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:32.67,ed2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ff80}{\frz-90}无人在此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:39.23,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H00ffff80}走った光操りながら
