Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:53.49,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H008080ff}忘れた笑顔 きっと二人なら取り戻す
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:53.49,ed2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H008080ff}{\frz-90}只要两人努力 一定能找回那遗忘的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:55.56,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ffff}気づいて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:55.56,ed2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ffff}{\frz-90}你要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:58.43,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ff80}I'm here waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:58.43,ed2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ff80}{\frz-90}我在这里等待着你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:01.55,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H00ffff80}今とは違う未来があっても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:01.55,ed2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H00ffff80}{\frz-90}即使身处不同的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:04.15,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0088aeff}I'm here waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:04.15,ed2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0088aeff}{\frz-90}我在这里等待着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:07.21,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H008080ff}叫び続けて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:07.21,ed2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H008080ff}{\frz-90}不停的呼喊着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:13.47,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ffff}きっと心は繋ぐ糸を手繰ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:13.47,ed2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ffff}{\frz-90}一定可以追寻回维系彼此心灵的纽带
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:18.52,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ff80}あの頃の私目を覚ますのように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:18.52,ed2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ff80}{\frz-90}等到那时请将我唤醒
